---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Group Retirement Savings Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Employer-sponsored group savings plans that help your team build financial security. Group RRSPs, DPSPs, and pension alternatives for Ontario businesses."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Investing</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Group Retirement Savings Plans</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        Help your employees build financial security — and attract the talent that stays. Group savings plans are one of the most valued benefits you can offer.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">A benefit that builds loyalty</h2>
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>A group retirement savings plan is an employer-sponsored program that makes it easier and more cost-effective for employees to save for retirement. It removes the friction of individual investing and — when employers match contributions — gives employees a meaningful reason to stay.</p>
        <p>We work with businesses of all sizes to design plans that fit their budget, their team's needs, and their administrative capacity. Whether you're setting up a plan for the first time or reviewing an existing arrangement, we'll walk you through every option.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Group RRSP</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">The most common employer savings vehicle. Employees contribute pre-tax dollars and investments grow tax-deferred. Employers can match contributions to incentivize participation and retention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Deferred Profit Sharing Plan (DPSP)</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Employer-funded profit-sharing contributions that vest over time. A powerful retention tool — employees stay to collect the benefit, and contributions are tax-deductible to the employer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Group TFSA</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">A workplace savings program that uses the tax-free savings structure. Employees make after-tax contributions that grow and can be withdrawn completely tax-free.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum p-6">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Combination plans</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[13px] text-brand-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Many employers use a Group RRSP + DPSP combination to maximize tax efficiency for both employer and employee. We design plans that work for both sides of the relationship.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-brand-tintPlum p-5 border-l-2 border-brand-plum/30">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">Mutual funds are offered through Investia Financial Services Inc. This article is for general information purposes only and does not constitute personalized financial or business advice. Please consult a qualified advisor before implementing any employee benefit program.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Set up a group savings plan for your team" sub="Book a free consultation to explore what options make sense for your business and employees." />

</BaseLayout>
